          "Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ibn Fazzal, from Abdullah Bin Maymoun Al Qaddah, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The Paradise is Prophibited unto the cuckold’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "8. Ahmad ibn Muhammad has narrated from ibn Faddal from ‘Abd Allah ibn Maymun who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Paradise is made unlawful for a pimp.”’ "
